{"tid":1633003,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"首次有人被控《禁蒙面法》 兩男女今提堂","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:28.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d27ff0e54c83832e0f940dfdcf6541b578734fb","tid":1633003,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:45:56.000Z","msg":"《禁止蒙面規例》上周六實施後，首次有人被控違例，今日提堂。<br />\n<br />\n警方上周六凌晨在藍田啟田道，發現有人非法集結及用雜物設置路障，企圖堵塞馬路。警員在現場拘捕一名18歲男子及一名38歲女子，兩人被暫控合共一項非法集結，以及各一項違反《禁止蒙面規例》罪，今日在東區裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2269461/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2269461%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4t8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=a1f95f2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2269461/</a>"},{"pid":"1401878ae3a2679d50244787831d86e3ca4986e4","tid":1633003,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:51:26.000Z","msg":"簡直係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31e64644d835394c93ebfb0ace78367daac2be20","tid":1633003,"uid":284636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:41:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>38歲女子</strong><br />\n過去popo主力拉後生<br />\n宜家拉口罩中年老年可以告蒙面"}]}